                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-8">11. How to Choose: Complete Decision Framework</h2>
                    
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">Use this structured approach to determine which manufacturing model fits your specific situation.</p>
                    
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">1</div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What's your total budget for this project?</h4>
                                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Under $20K:</strong> ODM is your realistic option. <strong>$20K-$50K:</strong> Hybrid approach works well. <strong>$50K+:</strong> Full OEM becomes viable with significant product differentiation.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">2</div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">How unique does your product need to be?</h4>
                                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Same function, better branding:</strong> ODM is sufficient. <strong>Unique features/technology:</strong> OEM required. <strong>Some differentiation, faster time:</strong> Hybrid is the answer.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">3</div>
