                                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Under 2 months:</strong> ODM only. <strong>2-4 months:</strong> ODM or Hybrid. <strong>4+ months:</strong> Any model works with proper planning.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">4</div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What's your order quantity?</h4>
